rows.label: tlk41310151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, there!
You've done so much for me recently,
I can't thank you enough.

rows.label: tlk41310151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Da's still under investigation, but it
looks like everything he's telling
them is the truth.

rows.label: tlk41310151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There's room for extenuating
circumstances, it seems. Maybe one
day, he'll be able to go back home.
